## Summary
This documentation page explains how to use Amplitude's Revenue LTV Chart to track monetization progress for new users over time (up to 12 months). It details the setup process, available metrics (Total Revenue, New Paying Users, ARPU, ARPPU), and configuration options for analyzing revenue data across different user segments.

